<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Cookie Policy - AI Buzz Media</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Learn about how AI Buzz Media uses cookies and similar technologies to enhance your browsing experience." />
  <link rel="canonical" href={Astro.url} />
</head>
<body>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="legal-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Cookie Policy</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Understanding how we use cookies and similar technologies</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="legal-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-wrapper">
          <div class="effective-date">
            <strong>Effective Date:</strong> 7/1/2025
          </div>
          
          <p class="intro">
            At AI Buzz Media, we respect your privacy and are committed to transparency about how we collect and use data to enhance your experience with our AI-focused content and services. This Cookie Policy explains our use of cookies and similar technologies on our website.
          </p>
          
          <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>Understanding Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
            
            <h3>What Are Cookies?</h3>
            <p>
              Cookies are small data files stored on your device when you visit our website. They help us recognize your browser, remember your preferences, and provide personalized experiences as you explore AI news, reviews, and educational content.
            </p>
            
            <h3>Similar Technologies</h3>
            <p>We also use related technologies including:</p>
            <ul class="tech-list">
              <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> For enhanced site functionality</li>
              <li><strong>Pixel Tags:</strong> To measure content engagement</li>
              <li><strong>Session Storage:</strong> For temporary data during your visit</li>
              <li><strong>Analytics Beacons:</strong> To understand user behavior patterns</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
          
          <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>How AI Buzz Media Uses Cookies</h2>
            <p>We categorize our cookie usage to ensure transparency:</p>
            
            <div class="cookie-categories">
              <div class="cookie-category essential">
                <div class="category-header">
                  <span class="category-icon">üîß</span>
                  <h3>Essential Cookies (Always Active)</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="category-content">
                  <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Core website functionality</p>
                  <h4>What They Do:</h4>
                  <ul class="category-list">
                    <li>Enable secure browsing and account access</li>
                    <li>Remember your consent preferences</li>
                    <li>Maintain shopping cart contents (for digital products)</li>
                    <li>Support comment systems and user interactions</li>
                    <li>Ensure proper page loading and navigation</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p><strong>Legal Basis:</strong> Necessary for legitimate interests in providing our service</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="cookie-category analytics">
                <div class="category-header">
                  <span class="category-icon">üìä</span>
                  <h3>Performance & Analytics Cookies</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="category-content">
                  <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Website optimization and content improvement</p>
                  <h4>What They Do:</h4>
                  <ul class="category-list">
                    <li>Track popular AI topics and article engagement</li>
                    <li>Measure page load times and technical performance</li>
                    <li>Identify trending content categories</li>
                    <li>Monitor search functionality effectiveness</li>
                    <li>Generate anonymous usage statistics</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p><strong>Partners:</strong> Google Analytics, Hotjar (anonymized data)</p>
                  <p><strong>Your Control:</strong> Can be disabled via cookie settings</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="cookie-category functional">
                <div class="category-header">
                  <span class="category-icon">‚öôÔ∏è</span>
                  <h3>Functional Cookies</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="category-content">
                  <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Enhanced user experience</p>
                  <h4>What They Do:</h4>
                  <ul class="category-list">
                    <li>Remember your preferred content categories</li>
                    <li>Save reading progress on long-form articles</li>
                    <li>Maintain dark/light mode preferences</li>
                    <li>Store newsletter subscription status</li>
                    <li>Enable social sharing functionality</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p><strong>Your Control:</strong> Can be disabled, but may affect site functionality</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="cookie-category marketing">
                <div class="category-header">
                  <span class="category-icon">üéØ</span>
                  <h3>Marketing & Advertising Cookies</h3>
                </div>
                <div class="category-content">
                  <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Relevant content recommendations and advertising</p>
                  <h4>What They Do:</h4>
                  <ul class="category-list">
                    <li>Show relevant AI tool recommendations</li>
                    <li>Measure affiliate link performance</li>
                    <li>Display personalized product suggestions</li>
                    <li>Track conversion rates for digital products</li>
                    <li>Enable retargeting for our educational content</li>
                  </ul>
                  <p><strong>Partners:</strong> Google Ads, Facebook Pixel, affiliate networks</p>
                  <p><strong>Your Control:</strong> Fully controllable via cookie preferences</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
          
          <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>Third-Party Services and Data Processing</h2>
            
            <div class="third-party-services">
              <div class="service-group">
                <h3>Analytics Providers:</h3>
                <ul class="service-list">
                  <li><strong>Google Analytics 4:</strong> Website traffic and user behavior analysis</li>
                  <li><strong>Microsoft Clarity:</strong> User session recordings and heatmaps</li>
                  <li><strong>Hotjar:</strong> User experience optimization</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="service-group">
                <h3>Advertising Partners:</h3>
                <ul class="service-list">
                  <li><strong>Google Ads:</strong> Targeted advertising and measurement</li>
                  <li><strong>Facebook/Meta:</strong> Social media integration and advertising</li>
                  <li><strong>Affiliate Networks:</strong> Commission tracking for product recommendations</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="service-group">
                <h3>Content Delivery:</h3>
                <ul class="service-list">
                  <li><strong>YouTube:</strong> Embedded AI tutorial videos</li>
                  <li><strong>Twitter/X:</strong> Social media content integration</li>
                  <li><strong>LinkedIn:</strong> Professional content sharing</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="data-protection-note">
              <p><strong>Data Protection:</strong> All third-party processors are GDPR-compliant and bound by data processing agreements.</p>
            </div>
          </section>
          
          <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>Your Privacy Rights and Controls</h2>
            
            <div class="privacy-controls">
              <div class="control-item">
                <span class="control-icon">üõ°Ô∏è</span>
                <div>
                  <h3>Cookie Consent Management</h3>
                  <ul class="control-list">
                    <li><strong>Initial Visit:</strong> You can accept or customize cookie preferences via our consent banner</li>
                    <li><strong>Ongoing Control:</strong> Access cookie settings anytime via the privacy icon in our footer</li>
                    <li><strong>Granular Options:</strong> Enable/disable specific cookie categories</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="control-item">
                <span class="control-icon">üîß</span>
                <div>
                  <h3>Browser-Level Controls</h3>
                  <ul class="control-list">
                    <li><strong>Chrome:</strong> Settings > Privacy & Security > Cookies</li>
                    <li><strong>Firefox:</strong> Options > Privacy & Security</li>
                    <li><strong>Safari:</strong> Preferences > Privacy</li>
                    <li><strong>Edge:</strong> Settings > Cookies and Site Permissions</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="control-item">
                <span class="control-icon">üåê</span>
                <div>
                  <h3>Industry Opt-Out Resources</h3>
                  <ul class="control-list">
                    <li><strong>Network Advertising Initiative (NAI):</strong> optout.networkadvertising.org</li>
                    <li><strong>Digital Advertising Alliance (DAA):</strong> optout.aboutads.info</li>
                    <li><strong>European Interactive Digital Advertising Alliance:</strong> youronlinechoices.eu</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
          
          <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>‚ö†Ô∏è Impact of Disabling Cookies</h2>
            
            <div class="impact-grid">
              <div class="impact-item positive">
                <h3>Minimal Impact:</h3>
                <ul class="impact-list">
                  <li>Core content remains fully accessible</li>
                  <li>AI news and articles load normally</li>
                  <li>Basic site navigation functions properly</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="impact-item negative">
                <h3>Potential Limitations:</h3>
                <ul class="impact-list">
                  <li>Personalized content recommendations may be less relevant</li>
                  <li>Site preferences may not be remembered between visits</li>
                  <li>Some interactive features may require re-authentication</li>
                  <li>Analytics help us improve content quality</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
          
          <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>Data Retention and Security</h2>
            
            <div class="retention-security">
              <div class="retention-info">
                <h3>Retention Periods:</h3>
                <ul class="retention-list">
                  <li><strong>Session Cookies:</strong> Deleted when you close your browser</li>
                  <li><strong>Persistent Cookies:</strong> 30 days to 2 years (varies by purpose)</li>
                  <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> 26 months (Google Analytics standard)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              
              <div class="security-info">
                <h3>Security Measures:</h3>
                <ul class="security-list">
                  <li>All cookies transmitted over secure HTTPS connections</li>
                  <li>Regular security audits of third-party integrations</li>
                  <li>Data minimization principles applied</li>
                  <li>No sensitive personal information stored in cookies</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </section>
          
          <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>International Data Transfers</h2>
            <p>
              Some third-party services may process data outside your country. We ensure appropriate safeguards:
            </p>
            <ul class="safeguards-list">
              <li>EU-US Data Privacy Framework compliance</li>
              <li>Standard Contractual Clauses with processors</li>
              <li>Adequacy Decisions recognition where applicable</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
          
          <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>Updates to This Policy</h2>
            <p><strong>Notification:</strong> Significant changes will be announced via:</p>
            <ul class="notification-list">
              <li>Prominent website notification</li>
              <li>Email notification to subscribers</li>
              <li>Updated effective date on this page</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Continued Use:</strong> Using our website after policy updates indicates acceptance of changes</p>
          </section>
          
          <section class="legal-section">
            <h2>Contact Information</h2>
            <p>Questions about cookies or privacy practices?</p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
              <h3>Contact Information:</h3>
              <p><strong>Email:</strong> contact@aibuzzmedia.com</p>
              <p><strong>Subject:</strong> Cookie Policy Inquiry</p>
              <p><strong>Response Time:</strong> Within 48 hours</p>
            </div>
            
            <p class="closing">
              Your privacy matters to us. By using cookies responsibly, we can continue providing valuable AI insights while respecting your preferences and protecting your data.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
  
